    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a Standards Track portion of the Management Information Base for use with network management protocols in the Internet community.  In particular, it describes managed objects for modeling of Pseudowire Edge-to-Edge services carried over a general Packet Switched Network. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
